Package org.jamsim.ascape.navigator

Ascape Navigator.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OutputNodeProvider
    Provider of a simulation output node for a given run number and/or at the end of the simulation.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    EndOfSimNodeProvider
    Provides a pre-existing DefaultMutableTreeNode at the end of all runs.
    MicroSimScapeNode
    Navigator tree node for a MicroSimScape.
    MicroSimTreeBuilder
    TreeBuilder that creates MicroSimScapeNode for MicroSimScape model elements, provides a PeformActionOnSelectedNode selection listener and same as DefaultTreeBuilder for everything else.
    OutputDatasetNodeProvider
    Connects an OutputDatasetProvider to a scape by adding any StatCollectors and/or charts to the scape and providing the dataset results as a output node for the Navigator.
    OutputNode
    A ScapeListener that displays Navigator output nodes after each iteration and/or at the end of the simulation.
    RecordedMicroSimTreeBuilder
    TreeBuilder that records nodes created so they can be fetched afterwards.
    SaveablePanelViewNode
    A Saveable PanelViewNode.
    SubFolderNode
    Navigator node that displays subfolders of nodes for simulation runs.
